{"tid":2030574,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[英文獨立口號] One Country，One Hong Kong！","createTime":"2020-05-22T23:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T03:15:33.000Z","uid":154486,"like":90,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdbd8ff237b995b55ccf7e1b7e1bbd3f91878e8","tid":2030574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:29:34.000Z","msg":"繼之前Stand With Hong Kong 之後，我發現原來英文口號真係越簡單越好<br />\n我諗到一個自覺幾好既<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">One Country</span></strong></span><br />\nB: <span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">One Hong Kong</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本身看似係攞一國兩制既英文<em>One Country, Two Systems</em>做修改<br />\n如果<strong>你覺得外國人會以為我地係要講一個中國，維護領土完整</strong>，就唔係太岩<br />\n但係其實係參考左著名<strong>美國大法官Oliver Wendell Holmes Jr.</strong>既名言：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>One flag,<br />\nOne land,<br />\nOne heart,<br />\nOne hand,<br />\nOne nation evermore.<br />\n</strong></div></span><br />\n呢句說話係美國獨立日入面經常講，如果要打國際牌，應該會得到更多美國人既支持"},{"pid":"b9c6cf9ed162a47b23a4b66de86d839819f91b66","tid":2030574,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"希望各位繼續諗一Ｄ簡單既英文口號<br />\n真係越簡單越好"},{"pid":"991a0dd1593567fb9fafe9c8acaf8e81e898ae67","tid":2030574,"uid":62721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"好，呢個正<br />\n大力推"},{"pid":"88f04e2bc428a2289690c05f5ba44cf0eceddc72","tid":2030574,"uid":62721,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:33:29.000Z","msg":"但會唔會俾人誤會， 一個中國裡面得一個香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df421aec27c1e7987f3788244938f6e575ed871d","tid":2030574,"uid":113074,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:34:39.000Z","msg":"咁撚弱智嘅嘢又嚟<br />\n<br />\n以前咪又係叫人唔好叫光復香港時代革命<br />\n走