KYrtpw%3D&h=a560ef1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%96%87%E6%91%98%2Farticle%2F20160507%2Fs00022%2F1462583417118%2F%E4%B9%9F%E8%AB%87%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%8F%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%BB%8E%E8%9D%B8%E8%97%A4%EF%BC%89&h=62cb8b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/文摘/article/20160507/s00022/1462583417118/也談民族與國族（文-黎蝸藤）</a><br />\n<br />\n國族： 孫中山在1924年三民主義演講中首次提出「國族」，中共棄用。<br />\n<br />\nethno-cultural nationalism中，民族是建立在包括共同語言、血緣、文化和傳統等客觀因素之上，故民族的存在先於國家（即民族國家，nation state）。"},{"pid":"f68bacb488e534ef01d9854765d2dc777879871d","tid":2030574,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a81680478312bb26906f5bc92301740d658624b","tid":2030574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085526ea95d56f92444b055f8cdb7863f8aa237a","tid":2030574,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2893c14316d0f35b19e9a310c4d67a8d756d3c0","tid":2030574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:15:15.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n如果中文用民族自強，香港獨立，順序意思完全Fit哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:19:15.000Z","msg":"中文就應該倒轉 wor 青 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文梗係最重要嗰部份行先 (中英文語句重點位置係啱啱相反的), 老西都叫香港獨立先。氣勢先出。話唔定叫叫下口號俾人打斷或者蓋過, 都叫到頭嗰句。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋通常觀眾係最接收到頭幾個字....傳媒影 sound bite 都係。<br />\n<strong>香港獨立，<br />\n民族自強！</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:20:49.000Z","msg":"之前已經有巴打講過，實際上「香港獨立」叫先係細聲Ｄ<br />\n第二句Ｄ人回應通常係大聲好多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:22:15.000Z","msg":"咁唯一出路都係呢個情況啦。<br />\n<br />\n實際上唔駛人帶, 有人叫第一聲, 之後全人類自動波啦。而家咩時勢仲要等人帶然後先回應咩.."},{"pid":"d27e54c11bc8e3